  "text": "The first mutation, substitution of leu for gly, creates the DAL motif found in isolate 3.3 of PPV (Lo! pez- and the second, substitution of ser for gly, reproduces the DAS motif found in PSbMV [CITATION_1] . No transmission of the DAL or DAS motif-containing mutants of TVMV was obtained in plant-to-plant transmission tests (Table  1) . A previously described DAA motif-containing TVMV mutant [CITATION_2] , which reproduces the motif present in PeMoV, exhibited very low transmission from plant to plant (Table 1) .",
